From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with author and lecturer in archaeoastronomy, astrotheology, ethnopharmacology, Jan Irvin. Mr. Irvin has lectured on mind control, logical fallacies,  and how to free one's mind from the current system of control. He will talk about the dumbing down of society and how mind control is used in advertising. 

Alex also covers the latest news on the faltering economy and the prospect of global world war as the United States and NATO prepare ground troops for a Libyan intervention.

Though not listed on the web site, Alex is also joined (hour 3) by "Jimmy Justice," an activist in New York City who posts videos of police breaking laws.
